document_data.caption: A map showing Aerynn's Street in Aithelar.
document_data.name: Aerynn's Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Aerynn's Street''' was a street found in the coastal town of [[Aithelar]] in [[Callidyrr]] on the [[Moonshae Isles]] in {{YearlinkName|1345}}.{{Cite interactive atlas}}
document_data.Location: Aerynn's Street connected and ran perpendicular to [[Bottle Lane]] and [[Callidyrr Ride]] near the center of Aithelar. It intersected [[Aithe High Street]] midway along its length.
